defaultA PROMISE TO LEARN, A COMMITMENT TO ACT AND A DUTY OF CANDOUR, DISCLOSURE AND OPENNESS
default225 final hearings came before a conduct and competence committee. 14 registrants had conditions of practice imposed, 40 had a caution imposed, 44 were struck off and 61 were suspended.
